        <summary class="list-none flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-stone-900 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-rose-500 shrink-0"></span>Pourquoi un mastermind et pas du coaching individuel ?</div>
